entry.title: Diabetes Dataset Report (2) -- Model Training And Evaluating
entry.summary: In the previous article, I did data preprocessing. It is often seen as one of the most important step during a machine learning project. One must be patient with the data manimulation no matter how troublesome it is. In this article, we are finally exposed to the model traing procedure. I will demonstrate how to conduct different types of classification models and how to evalute their performance.
